text.tspan: Actions that are not used often
Mix favorites and non-favorites stations when searching. Always
priorities favorite stations first. When a user find a station
they like they can play it, which adds it to their favorites.
Quick access to action buttons when the song is currently playing.
Users are more likely to "Like" or "Share" a song when it's currently playing.
Songs not currently playing have the on-hover action menu, staying out of the way till needed.
